Author: michaelneale
Content: If my memory serves correct, back when DOS was around it was a Zoo of many Oses, basically each hardware platform had some variant and very incompatible OS. So I think that part of the analogy holds.

Author: andyn
Content:
There seems to be a group of people intent on submitting everything that appears on reddit or digg and it's sad.

Can't we get more unique links rather than this whole sloshing around of whatever's going around as email attachments?

Author: marcus
Content:
Lets try to stick to something ethical with either a positive impact on the world or at least without a negative one.

Don't want the spam in the worlds Inboxes to be on my hands.
